WEBVTT

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary Diaries</b></font>

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:33.980
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:38.450 --> 00:01:42.410
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}<font size="16">Episode 30: The Crystal Pavilion, for the Third Time</font></font>

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:40.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Someone wants to see me?</font>

00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:42.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}A court lady from the clinic?</font>

00:01:43.140 --> 00:01:45.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, she wants to meet you, Maomao.</font>

00:01:46.670 --> 00:01:51.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sorry. I should have taken the medicine
 you made for me while I was here,</font>

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:55.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but she saw me take it last night.</font>

00:01:56.260 --> 00:02:00.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This could be trouble. Only doctors
 are allowed to make medicine.</font>

00:02:00.980 --> 00:02:02.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My apologies.</font>

00:02:02.930 --> 00:02:04.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Will there be repercussions?</font>

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:06.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, no, that's...</font>

00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:07.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's just...</font>

00:02:10.410 --> 00:02:11.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Just tell me.</font>

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes...</font>

00:02:14.390 --> 00:02:18.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She wants to borrow Maomao for a while.</font>

00:02:18.620 --> 00:02:19.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao?</font>

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:26.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Ailan, please bring Yinghua here.</font>

00:02:26.540 --> 00:02:28.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh? Y-Yes.</font>

00:02:35.260 --> 00:02:38.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I've been summoned.</i></font>

00:02:41.620 --> 00:02:43.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's hurry.</font>

00:02:43.980 --> 00:02:46.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>With a chaperone, too.</i></font>

00:02:49.710 --> 00:02:51.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My name is Shenlü.</font>

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:54.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Green-tinted eyes...</i></font>

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is she from the western region, 
like Lady Gyokuyou?</i></font>

00:02:58.150 --> 00:03:00.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She seemed like a "tough 
mother hen" type yesterday,</i></font>

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:04.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but in a calm setting, she gives 
a wise, reserved impression.</i></font>

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:07.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>At any rate, this is intimidating, 
with the nice tea and everything.</i></font>

00:03:07.850 --> 00:03:10.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please excuse me for my attitude yesterday.</font>

00:03:10.730 --> 00:03:13.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I had no idea you worked 
for the Precious Consort.</font>

00:03:13.380 --> 00:03:14.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's fine.</font>

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:17.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Precious Consort" is the rank name 
for Lady Gyokuyou.</i></font>

00:03:17.630 --> 00:03:21.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Court ladies from outside the pavilion 
often use these titles.</i></font>

00:03:22.130 --> 00:03:25.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I asked you to visit me to ask for your help.</font>

00:03:26.910 --> 00:03:27.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:32.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There is a servant working for the Wise 
Consort, Lady Lihua, at the Crystal Pavilion.</font>

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'd like for you to make some medicine for her.</font>

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:39.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you understand what you're saying?!</font>

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:42.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If people find out that someone 
who's not a doctor is making medicines...!</font>

00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:45.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm quite aware.</font>

00:03:45.060 --> 00:03:45.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What...</font>

00:03:45.730 --> 00:03:47.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sure you have your reasons.</font>

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao?!</font>

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:50.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please, continue.</font>

00:03:51.650 --> 00:03:53.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you sure?</font>

00:03:57.730 --> 00:03:59.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Can you explain the circumstances?</font>

00:04:00.750 --> 00:04:02.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you.</font>

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:07.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's a servant girl who frequented this
 laundry area who I became familiar with.</font>

00:04:08.210 --> 00:04:12.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Around the time the caravan came, 
she seemed to be fatigued and had a fever.</font>

00:04:13.260 --> 00:04:16.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She also had this strange cough.</font>

00:04:18.170 --> 00:04:22.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I told her to get some serious rest,</font>

00:04:22.370 --> 00:04:25.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but after that, she suddenly went missing.</font>

00:04:25.730 --> 00:04:27.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did she start using 
a different laundry area,</font>

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:29.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">or was tasked with something else, perhaps?</font>

00:04:29.790 --> 00:04:33.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even so, that cough 
needs to be properly looked at.</font>

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:36.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So she hasn't even visited the clinic?</font>

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:40.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Correct. Perhaps her 
higher-ups didn't allow it.</font>

00:04:40.970 --> 00:04:43.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's the bad part of the Crystal Pavilion.</i></font>

00:04:43.930 --> 00:04:45.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If a servant girl had to ask for permission,</i></font>

00:04:45.890 --> 00:04:48.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>she'd have to go to the head
 lady-in-waiting, not Lady Lihua.</i></font>

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:51.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's quite likely that 
she asked but was ignored.</i></font>

00:04:51.930 --> 00:04:55.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's already been half a month 
since I last saw her.</font>

00:04:56.300 --> 00:04:57.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Half a month?!</font>

00:05:01.460 --> 00:05:03.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is getting troublesome.</font>

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:07.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Does this servant girl really even exist?</font>

00:05:07.390 --> 00:05:09.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think it does warrant investigation.</font>

00:05:10.330 --> 00:05:11.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A weird cough...</i></font>

00:05:11.870 --> 00:05:14.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If it's contagious, 
we have to do something, fast.</i></font>

00:05:14.620 --> 00:05:17.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's not a problem that limits itself 
to the Crystal Pavilion.</i></font>

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:21.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I know these types of things catch your eye,</font>

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:24.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but make sure you get 
the right permissions first.</font>

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You have a bad habit of 
diving into things head-first.</font>

00:05:27.970 --> 00:05:28.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:05:29.130 --> 00:05:30.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have to be patient.</i></font>

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:35.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'll first ask Master Jinshi to make the 
introduction, but for now, what I can do is...</i></font>

00:05:38.030 --> 00:05:40.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What?! M-Maomao?!</font>

00:05:41.580 --> 00:05:43.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Come on, what did I just say?!</font>

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:47.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sorry. I found something I was looking for, 
and couldn't control myself.</font>

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:50.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What were you looking for?</font>

00:05:50.030 --> 00:05:50.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's this.</font>

00:05:51.260 --> 00:05:54.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Unfortunately, the main body got away.</font>

00:05:55.710 --> 00:05:58.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm making a drug to make it 
grow back. To do that...</i></font>

00:05:58.950 --> 00:06:02.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I want to study how a tail 
that fell off can grow back...</font>

00:06:02.620 --> 00:06:05.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh? Lady Yinghua?</font>

00:06:26.190 --> 00:06:27.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where are you going?</font>

00:06:28.350 --> 00:06:29.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin...</font>

00:06:30.550 --> 00:06:32.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're supposed to clean the main building.</font>

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:34.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you trying to go to that place again?</font>

00:06:35.390 --> 00:06:37.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I, um...</font>

00:06:37.220 --> 00:06:40.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I told you many times, mind your own business.</font>

00:06:41.220 --> 00:06:45.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I-I'm sorry! I'm truly, truly...</font>

00:06:46.130 --> 00:06:50.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin! The doctor from
 the medical office is here...</font>

00:06:50.310 --> 00:06:51.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The doctor?</font>

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:54.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What does he want now?</font>

00:06:54.700 --> 00:06:57.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He couldn't save the prince.</font>

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:02.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How may I help you?</font>

00:07:02.590 --> 00:07:05.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Um... I'd like to meet with the Wise Consort.</font>

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:13.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sorry. I don't think Lady Lihua 
wants to see you at all.</font>

00:07:13.970 --> 00:07:15.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">B-But...</font>

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:21.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What a tall... Have I ever seen 
this court lady before?</i></font>

00:07:26.300 --> 00:07:28.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I do have a document for the request.</font>

00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:30.840
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#151515"><b>Jinshi</b></font>

00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:34.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand. Please, this way.</font>

00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:38.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not to overstep, but Lady Lihua is quite well.</font>

00:07:39.050 --> 00:07:41.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, um, that's good to hear.</font>

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:45.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sure her great helpers support her well.</font>

00:07:45.470 --> 00:07:46.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That goes without saying.</font>

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:50.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">All who work at the Crystal Pavilion 
were born and raised in noble families.</font>

00:07:50.110 --> 00:07:53.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They truly deserve their spot 
in the emperor's service.</font>

00:07:53.470 --> 00:07:57.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Lihua is a noble from 
the imperial lineage, as well.</font>

00:07:57.910 --> 00:08:00.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Which also applies to me, and yet...</i></font>

00:08:01.540 --> 00:08:06.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">For our family, it is important for you 
to earn the love of the emperor.</font>

00:08:06.460 --> 00:08:09.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you understand, Lihua, Shin?</font>

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:10.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:08:11.550 --> 00:08:13.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Yet, why...</i></font>

00:08:19.470 --> 00:08:20.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is something wrong?</font>

00:08:22.650 --> 00:08:26.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, um... I was just wondering 
what that shed was.</font>

00:08:28.750 --> 00:08:31.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's just for storage.</font>

00:08:33.850 --> 00:08:36.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did you do any gardening in the area recently?</font>

00:08:37.850 --> 00:08:39.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, not in particular.</font>

00:08:40.830 --> 00:08:43.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Was that garden bush always there?</i></font>

00:08:44.790 --> 00:08:47.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're wearing perfume today.</font>

00:08:47.070 --> 00:08:47.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh...?</font>

00:08:48.570 --> 00:08:49.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin.</font>

00:08:51.620 --> 00:08:56.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pardon me for staying out of touch, 
and for what happened the other day.</font>

00:08:59.300 --> 00:09:01.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're from back then...!</font>

00:09:03.910 --> 00:09:04.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait!</font>

00:09:06.530 --> 00:09:07.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you...</font>

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:14.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Little lady!</font>

00:09:26.290 --> 00:09:29.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I need hot water! 
Please go boil some hot water!</font>

00:09:29.620 --> 00:09:31.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">G-Got it!</font>

00:09:39.430 --> 00:09:40.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Drink this, slowly.</font>

00:09:48.690 --> 00:09:50.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why is she being treated like this?</font>

00:09:51.220 --> 00:09:53.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why not?</font>

00:09:53.740 --> 00:09:58.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Isn't it common sense to quarantine a sick 
person to make sure the illness doesn't spread?</font>

00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:02.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">True, this is a contagious
 disease, though it's weak.</font>

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:07.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But if you keep treating her 
like this, she will die.</font>

00:10:08.500 --> 00:10:13.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not that the death of a single servant girl 
would be much trouble for you.</font>

00:10:16.770 --> 00:10:19.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Coming back here reminded me
 of what happened before,</font>

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:22.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">when Lady Lihua was sick and bedridden.</font>

00:10:22.970 --> 00:10:27.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You were burning incense, 
as if to hide the smell of the sick.</font>

00:10:28.340 --> 00:10:29.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's your point?</font>

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:33.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I felt the exact opposite this time.</font>

00:10:33.330 --> 00:10:37.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You've placed a sick person here 
to hide the scent of the incense.</font>

00:10:42.030 --> 00:10:42.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stop!</font>

00:10:45.420 --> 00:10:49.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The ladies at the Crystal Pavilion 
have too many secrets.</font>

00:10:50.580 --> 00:10:54.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Look, so many trade goods from the 
caravan that were banned the other day.</font>

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:59.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Another poor eunuch is going to get a whipping.</font>

00:10:59.370 --> 00:11:00.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Don't let her shake me.</i></font>

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:07.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even though each single item 
is too weak as a poison,</font>

00:11:07.860 --> 00:11:10.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">what would happen if they mixed together?</font>

00:11:10.430 --> 00:11:14.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's no way this girl can 
figure out my true goals...!</i></font>

00:11:14.860 --> 00:11:16.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin.</font>

00:11:17.450 --> 00:11:21.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why are you trying to make an abortion drug?</font>

00:11:34.090 --> 00:11:37.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If I knew I was going to find it on 
the first visit, I didn't need the disguise.</i></font>

00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:42.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Since they knew my face, I was
 afraid this could take a long time.</i></font>

00:11:45.810 --> 00:11:50.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you for waiting, 
and for the clothes to change into.</font>

00:11:51.050 --> 00:11:56.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's fine. We can't have you wearing
clothes you wore to treat the sick.</font>

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:59.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Now, let's go. Everyone is waiting.</font>

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:13.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What is the meaning of this, Lady Shin?</font>

00:12:13.820 --> 00:12:18.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Some items from the caravan were to be 
confiscated, as they could make poisons.</font>

00:12:18.930 --> 00:12:20.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That was the clear directive.</font>

00:12:23.250 --> 00:12:25.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Silence, huh?</i></font>

00:12:25.220 --> 00:12:28.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm surprised she can maintain that 
attitude even towards Master Jinshi.</i></font>

00:12:28.870 --> 00:12:34.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Shin. Head lady-in-waiting at the 
Crystal Pavilion, and Lady Lihua's cousin.</i></font>

00:12:34.890 --> 00:12:39.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She looks a bit like Lady Lihua. 
A beautiful woman, clearly full of pride.</i></font>

00:12:40.060 --> 00:12:42.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That must be why she's 
the head lady-in-waiting.</i></font>

00:12:43.990 --> 00:12:47.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Beautiful flowers attract the most 
attention when gathered in one spot.</i></font>

00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:49.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Given her status, it wouldn't be unnatural to</i></font>

00:12:49.810 --> 00:12:51.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>have her serve as a mid-rank concubine herself.</i></font>

00:12:51.840 --> 00:12:54.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm sure she's well aware of that, as well.</i></font>

00:12:55.260 --> 00:12:56.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's change the question.</font>

00:12:57.510 --> 00:13:00.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What were you trying to do 
with these banned goods?</font>

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:03.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't know what you're talking about.</font>

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:07.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's true, I ordered the sick servant 
to sleep inside the separate shed.</font>

00:13:08.180 --> 00:13:10.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But that was to prevent 
the spread of the disease.</font>

00:13:11.640 --> 00:13:14.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I had no idea what was in there.</font>

00:13:15.150 --> 00:13:17.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How is that a crime?</font>

00:13:19.010 --> 00:13:22.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Quarantining the servant girl 
in the shed was not a crime.</i></font>

00:13:23.210 --> 00:13:26.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's unavoidable. That's just how low 
the value of the life of a servant is.</i></font>

00:13:26.430 --> 00:13:27.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">On the other hand,</font>

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:32.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">for them to suddenly barge in here 
demanding to see Lady Lihua,</font>

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:35.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">only to then start ransacking 
our shed, is somehow not a problem?</font>

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:41.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In fact, the only reason anyone 
went to that place was to feed the sick.</font>

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:45.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Conversely, anyone could be there at any time.</font>

00:13:45.230 --> 00:13:48.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How can you prove that 
these items belonged to me?</font>

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:51.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can ask the servant who was there.</font>

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:58.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The testimony of a barely conscious, 
feverish servant? Is that trustworthy?</font>

00:13:59.170 --> 00:14:01.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So you were aware that she's feverish.</font>

00:14:03.650 --> 00:14:09.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How kind of you to check in 
on the health of a lowly servant.</font>

00:14:10.060 --> 00:14:14.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then, it's no surprise that you have 
the smell of incense on you.</font>

00:14:15.570 --> 00:14:19.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even though you had no such scent before.</font>

00:14:20.830 --> 00:14:23.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I can't overstep any more.</i></font>

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:26.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I know that, but...</i></font>

00:14:28.220 --> 00:14:30.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Sometimes, I can get angry, too.</i></font>

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:35.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin, you have the same 
smell as this oil today.</font>

00:14:37.090 --> 00:14:40.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This bottle was placed inside a suitcase.</font>

00:14:40.550 --> 00:14:43.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is the smell strong enough 
to emanate outside of a closed box?</font>

00:14:44.590 --> 00:14:48.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May I check, just to be sure?</font>

00:14:52.700 --> 00:14:54.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">D-Don't touch me!</font>

00:14:55.370 --> 00:14:56.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Apothecary!</font>

00:14:58.770 --> 00:15:00.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's no big deal.</font>

00:15:01.060 --> 00:15:05.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're right. I had no right to lay
my hands upon you.</font>

00:15:06.870 --> 00:15:09.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's have someone else investigate.</font>

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:15.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Perhaps I could take over from here?</font>

00:15:17.730 --> 00:15:18.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Concubine Lihua...</i></font>

00:15:19.980 --> 00:15:22.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What would her punishment be?</font>

00:15:22.830 --> 00:15:25.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If she were truly trying 
to make an abortion drug,</font>

00:15:25.480 --> 00:15:27.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">it would be the same as 
murdering the emperor's child.</font>

00:15:27.900 --> 00:15:31.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And that would be the same, regardless 
of which concubine's child it was?</font>

00:15:31.140 --> 00:15:31.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Of course.</font>

00:15:35.310 --> 00:15:39.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even if Shin's target was me?</font>

00:15:40.510 --> 00:15:42.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Concubine Lihua! That's...</font>

00:15:43.390 --> 00:15:45.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I get it now.</i></font>

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:49.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Lihua's outfit is similar 
to the one Lady Gyokuyou is wearing.</i></font>

00:15:50.730 --> 00:15:53.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No wonder the ladies-in-waiting 
here are no good.</i></font>

00:15:53.730 --> 00:15:55.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's not Lady Lihua's fault.</i></font>

00:15:55.720 --> 00:15:59.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>These types of women were
 gathered here intentionally...</i></font>

00:15:59.930 --> 00:16:02.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>by the head lady-in-waiting, Shin.</i></font>

00:16:02.520 --> 00:16:08.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shin, you've never treated me as a concubine.</font>

00:16:10.010 --> 00:16:11.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm not worthy of becoming an empress dowager.</font>

00:16:11.900 --> 00:16:13.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's what you thought, right?</font>

00:16:14.590 --> 00:16:18.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We didn't know until the last moment 
which one of us, you or I,</font>

00:16:19.660 --> 00:16:21.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">would become the concubine.</font>

00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:28.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What, now you're talking down to me?</font>

00:16:30.550 --> 00:16:33.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's what I've always hated about you!</font>

00:16:34.100 --> 00:16:36.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was always better at my studies 
and manners than you!</font>

00:16:37.060 --> 00:16:41.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And I excel in so many more things than you!</font>

00:16:41.770 --> 00:16:44.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And yet, why does everyone...!</font>

00:16:45.090 --> 00:16:50.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's a huge gap in breast size... 
I mean, caliber as a concubine.</i></font>

00:16:51.180 --> 00:16:53.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Lihua" and "Shin". "Pear" and "Apricot."</i></font>

00:16:53.980 --> 00:16:57.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's like they named them to pair up with 
each other, with high status and education.</i></font>

00:16:58.120 --> 00:17:03.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Still, there are fools who let their emotions 
control them, to the point of grave mistakes.</i></font>

00:17:04.220 --> 00:17:07.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I guess Lady Shin is just one of those people.</i></font>

00:17:07.830 --> 00:17:10.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Because you're the daughter 
of the head of the family?</font>

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:13.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is that why you're better than me?! It can't be!</font>

00:17:13.600 --> 00:17:17.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've been raised to become 
the empress from the day I was born!</font>

00:17:18.390 --> 00:17:20.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May I consider that a confession?</font>

00:17:24.360 --> 00:17:28.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May you rot childlessly in this garden, Lihua!</font>

00:17:34.910 --> 00:17:40.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't touch me! Unhand me, 
you filthy eunuch! Let go!</font>

00:17:41.670 --> 00:17:45.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Shin, you must love the emperor very much.</font>

00:17:46.260 --> 00:17:49.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Of course I do! What are you saying?!</font>

00:17:49.210 --> 00:17:52.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, I just thought...</font>

00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:57.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">you seemed to love
 the status of empress more,</font>

00:17:58.420 --> 00:18:00.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">unlike Lady Lihua.</font>

00:18:02.270 --> 00:18:03.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What...</font>

00:18:15.370 --> 00:18:18.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, that's how you felt, Shin.</font>

00:18:26.160 --> 00:18:31.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sir Jinshi, this head lady-in-waiting 
has verbally abused her mistress.</font>

00:18:31.820 --> 00:18:34.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Enough to make me raise my hand against her.</font>

00:18:34.490 --> 00:18:37.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As such, I will fire her from my service.</font>

00:18:37.060 --> 00:18:38.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Concubine Lihua? That's...</font>

00:18:38.890 --> 00:18:41.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, is the slap not enough?</font>

00:18:42.740 --> 00:18:44.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In that case, how about this...</font>

00:18:44.180 --> 00:18:45.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please wait!</font>

00:18:45.390 --> 00:18:46.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will not!</font>

00:18:47.660 --> 00:18:50.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Well played. She's no longer 
how she was in the past.</i></font>

00:18:51.940 --> 00:18:56.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She's no longer the fading, frail woman, 
waiting for her life's thread to sever itself.</i></font>

00:18:57.160 --> 00:19:01.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please ban her from ever 
entering the rear palace again.</font>

00:19:01.810 --> 00:19:03.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A lenient and generous punishment,</i></font>

00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:06.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but probably enough of 
a humiliation for this woman.</i></font>

00:19:06.850 --> 00:19:09.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even if she feels resentment, 
she won't be able to do anything,</i></font>

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:12.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>after being chased out of 
the rear palace due to a scandal.</i></font>

00:19:13.290 --> 00:19:16.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>These two will never stand 
next to each other again.</i></font>

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:21.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Use this.</font>

00:19:23.970 --> 00:19:25.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're bleeding.</font>

00:19:25.500 --> 00:19:27.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm fine. It's just
some small cuts.</font>

00:19:28.300 --> 00:19:29.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's not the issue!</font>

00:19:32.420 --> 00:19:35.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I don't want to get blood on such fine silk...</i></font>

00:19:36.510 --> 00:19:39.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How did you figure out that 
the sick servant was in the shed?</font>

00:19:39.770 --> 00:19:44.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Given how you went in with a disguise, 
you didn't know at first, did you?</font>

00:19:44.950 --> 00:19:47.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I had some idea beforehand.</font>

00:19:48.170 --> 00:19:49.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Since she was sick,</font>

00:19:49.260 --> 00:19:52.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">she'd be somewhere out of sight, 
away from the others' bedrooms.</font>

00:19:53.060 --> 00:19:55.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I would never have thought 
it would be a storage shed, though.</font>

00:19:56.250 --> 00:19:59.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, there was a clue.</font>

00:20:00.040 --> 00:20:01.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That garden bush?</font>

00:20:01.850 --> 00:20:05.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. That flower is usually mostly red.</font>

00:20:05.860 --> 00:20:08.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But it's only white right now.</font>

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:10.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Someone must have 
picked it out and planted it there.</font>

00:20:11.070 --> 00:20:15.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In feng shui, they say green and white is 
a combination that brings good health.</font>

00:20:15.320 --> 00:20:16.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:20:17.100 --> 00:20:21.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That said, it's quite ironic that 
they chose the white blossom.</font>

00:20:21.780 --> 00:20:23.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">White blossom?</font>

00:20:23.410 --> 00:20:27.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The white powder packed in the seeds 
can be used to induce an abortion.</font>

00:20:29.130 --> 00:20:30.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They're all over the place!</font>

00:20:30.970 --> 00:20:34.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They're harmless, unless you know 
precisely how to make the medicine.</font>

00:20:34.440 --> 00:20:36.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Just like the scented oils from today.</font>

00:20:39.060 --> 00:20:43.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How did Lady Shin know that the scented 
oils could be used as an abortion drug?</font>

00:20:44.150 --> 00:20:47.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A trade good brought in 
by the caravan, no less.</font>

00:20:48.610 --> 00:20:52.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I doubt she'd confess 
even if questioned, but...</font>

00:20:52.750 --> 00:20:55.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Apothecary, can I ask you one thing?</font>

00:20:56.760 --> 00:20:58.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you saying that someone in this rear palace</font>

00:20:58.620 --> 00:21:02.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">is spreading the word that these oils
can be used for abortions?</font>

00:21:03.750 --> 00:21:04.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't know.</font>

00:21:05.250 --> 00:21:08.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But we can never be too careful.</font>

00:21:13.710 --> 00:21:15.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">U-Um...</font>

00:21:18.740 --> 00:21:20.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">White blossom...</font>

00:21:20.690 --> 00:21:23.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What happened to the girl in the shed?</font>

00:21:23.300 --> 00:21:26.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's leaving the rear palace 
to get proper treatment.</font>

00:21:26.930 --> 00:21:31.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Lihua offered it. She felt responsible.</i></font>

00:21:31.160 --> 00:21:33.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She's even paying the costs herself.</i></font>

00:21:34.770 --> 00:21:36.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:21:48.070 --> 00:21:50.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It seems like that apothecary was here again.</font>

00:21:50.900 --> 00:21:54.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. You must know everything.</font>

00:21:54.450 --> 00:21:56.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She has done nothing but save me.</font>

00:22:02.900 --> 00:22:04.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is something wrong?</font>

00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:08.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No...</font>

00:23:45.020 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22">{\an7}Next Time</font>

00:23:56.080 --> 00:23:59.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>{\an8}Next time: 
"The Shrine of Choosing."</i></font>

00:23:56.330 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}<font size="18">Episode 31: The Shrine of Choosing</font></font>

